          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Taxpayer Handouts to Illegal Immigrants Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits any state government that provides monetary payments to undocumented immigrants from receiving funds made available under the American Rescue Plan Act of 2021. <br> <br> If a state made such prohibited payments after the enactment of the American Rescue Plan Act of 2021 but before the enactment of this bill, the state must immediately pay to the federal government the amount equal to the sum of the prohibited payments.</p>]]>
          </text>
          <updateDate>2021-04-13T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
